features: Realistic Airplane Model with Stickers: Kids can imagine themselves as a pilot, flying the plane to take off, drive and land, giving your children a fun and unforgettable playtime. Grab your child's attention with the super cool flashing LED lights and the real jet engine sound of the airplane toy, which can be turned on and off at any time.With exquisite and high-quality stickers, children can unleash their imagination and creativity, decorate their own big planes, and give them a different experience!

Bump and Go Action: Not used for other model airplanes, this Airbus plane toy has an intelligent built-in "bump and move" system that is very advanced and premium. When it's about to hit an obstacle while traveling, it will turn to the right and will redirect itself to prevent collisions and damage.

Learning & Fun Airplane Toys: When the plane starts successfully, it will emit colorful and dazzling lights and a variety of lively music. These toys with lights and sounds will allow your children to learn about flying and motor skills, and help them develop creativity and imagination and stimulate their brain development. They are ideal playthings for toddlers, boys and girls to learn, grow and explore so they can have fun and grow while playing.

Ideal Kids Gift:Our large model airplane toy requires 3 AA batteries to be installed, just put the batteries in, press the start button and the plane is ready to fly! The surface is smooth and burr-free, which will not cause harm to toddlers skin. As a gift for birthday, party, Easter, Halloween, Christmas, New Year, it's a perfect choice to bring endless joy to your kids girls boys!
After-sales service: If you encounter any problems during the purchase or use, please feel free to contact us, we will help you within 24 hours.
